'''博羅市場'''（{{lang-en|Borough Market}}）是位於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[南華克倫敦自治市|南華克]]的一座食品批發和零售[[市場|市場]]。博羅市場是倫敦規模最大，歷史最久的食品市場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.visitlondon.com/attractions/shopping/markets/food-markets|title=Food markets in London|work=Visitlondon.com|date=|accessdate=2012-09-06|archive-date=2012-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601022622/http://www.visitlondon.com/attractions/shopping/markets/food-markets|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Lina|last=Goldberg|url=http://travel.cnn.com/explorations/shop/worlds-best-fresh-markets-316265|title=10 of the world's best fresh markets|work=CNN Travel|date=24 February 2013|accessdate=24 February 2013|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603082326/http://travel.cnn.com/explorations/shop/worlds-best-fresh-markets-316265/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，銷售多種來自世界各地的食品<ref name=bmti>{{cite web |url=http://www.london-traveltips.com/borough-market.htm |title=Borough Market Tourist Info |publisher=London-traveltips.com |date=2011-12-07 |accessdate=2012-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627014140/http://www.london-traveltips.com/borough-market.htm |archivedate=2012-06-27 }}</ref>。零售市場在每週三和週四的10點至17點；週五10點至18點；週六8點至17點營業。批發市場在每週一至週五的2點至8點營業。

[[2017年6月伦敦袭击事件|2017年6月伦敦袭击事件]]中，三名袭击者驾车在伦敦桥冲撞行人后，逃入市场，持刀袭击多人，最终被警方击毙<ref name="bbclive">{{cite web|title=BBC News Live|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-40147014|accessdate=3 June 2017|archive-date=2017-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626122536/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-40147014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

